* main - function that copies contents of a file to another file
* @argc: number of arguments parsed to the program
* @argv: array of argument pointers.
* Return: 0 on sucess.
* Description: If argument count is incorrect - exit code 97.
* If file_from does not exist or cannot be read - exit code 98
* 